{
  "stem": "5559.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you put him on there, no cloth, nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You cover him up with the tallits.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know, it's a bad road up the hill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a long way to Tipperary, so to speak, because it's about 10 kilometer, again, up to the Jewish cemetery, right?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I go, and my mother goes, in the deep snow, schlepping along.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took a long time-- no funeral, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't even [INAUDIBLE] if father was still alive here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody know, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The uncles weren't there, around, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Next of kin-- yeah, if I have another brother, so, probably would go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Your mother and this-- that's all you were allowed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The legs, covered this, and the legs are hanging over, and they shake.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Never forget this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is a terrible picture to see, you know, a person who's dead that's shaking like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Coming up, there were two more peasants with, you know-- with anything they had, because it was all frozen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you couldn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they brought heavy stuff, and shovels with the-- you know, the old [INAUDIBLE] graves, helped me put my father in, covered him with the tallits again, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, again, still, we organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Somehow, my mother couldn't care, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That [INAUDIBLE] is.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's why she survived, maybe also too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But she gave away, again, whatever she had, and there was a stone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we made him a real matzevah, a real stone, in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, it's there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I've never been back, naturally, since 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But it's supposed to be on the cemetery with the name carved, Bronstein, Hebrew, the date of when he died, and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's how I buried my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we lived the best we could, and Clipper start helping out.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
